<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3519125>
    dc:description "FIGURES 70–81. Caledonispa sarasini (Heller, 1916). 70. Body of male dorsal, 71. Body of female dorsal, 72. Antenna, 73. Frontoclypeus and prosternum, 74. Head of male dorsal, 75. Head of female dorsal, 76. Pronotum, 77. Mid leg of male, 78. Mid leg of female, 79. Fore leg of male, 80. Fore leg of female, 81. Lectotype labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3519125/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3519121>
    dc:description "FIGURES 51–60. Caledonispa panieensis sp. nov., dark form. 51. Body dorsal, 52. Antenna, 53. Frontoclypeus and prosternum, 54. Head of male dorsal, 55. Head of female dorsal, 56. Pronotum, 57. Fore leg of male, 58. Fore leg of female, 59. Mid leg of male, 60. Mid leg of female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3519121/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3519123>
    dc:description "FIGURES 61–69. Caledonispa panieensis sp. nov., pale form. 61. Body dorsal, 62.Antenna, 63. Head of male dorsal, 64. Head of female dorsal, 65. Pronotum, 66. Fore leg of male, 67. Fore leg of female, 68. Mid leg of male, 69. Mid leg of female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3519123/files/figure.png" ;
